    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000554/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description "This course deals with the fundamentals and applications of experimental techniques in structural engineering. This course is divided into three parts: the first part is aimed at the study of instrumentaion techniques and equipment; the second part deals with the design of load tests in bridges and buildings; the goal of the last part is the study of dynamic testing techniques."@es ;
